aceXi\">{{cite news |last=Griffiths |first=James |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/23/asia/wuhan-china-coronavirus-sars-response-intl-hnk/index.html |title=Wuhan is the latest crisis to face China's Xi, and it's exposing major flaws in his model of control |access-date=10 February 2020 |url-status=live |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200208194710/https://www.cnn.com/2020/01/23/asia/wuhan-china-coronavirus-sars-response-intl-hnk/index.html |archive-date=8 February 2020 |publisher=[[CNN.com|CNN]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"ThomReut_SKorea_zombie\">{{cite news |last1=Shin |first1=Hyonhee |last2=Cha |first2=Sangmi |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-china-health-southkorea-cases/like-a-zombie-apocalypse-residents-on-edge-as-coronavirus-cases-surge-in-south-korea-idUSKBN20E04F |title='Like a zombie apocalypse': Residents on edge as coronavirus cases surge in South Korea |date=20 February 2020 |access-date=20 February 2020 |url-status=live |archive-url= https://archive.today/D1K5i |archive-date=20 February 2020 |agency=[[Thomson Reuters]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"b82186\">{{Cite news |url=https://en.yna.co.kr/view/AEN20200229004000315 |title=42 Shincheonji followers came to S. Korea from virus-hit Wuhan over 8 months: gov't |date=29 February 2020 |agency=[[Yonhap News Agency]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"koreabiomed\">{{cite news |last1=Lee |first1=Han-soo |url=http://www.koreabiomed.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=7489 |title=COVID-19 patients soar to 204 in Korea |date=21 February 2020 |work=Korea Biomedical Review |access-date=21 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"science20200317\">{{cite journal |journal=Science |url=https://www.sciencemag.org/news/2020/03/coronavirus-cases-have-dropped-sharply-south-korea-whats-secret-its-success |title=Coronavirus cases have dropped sharply in South Korea. What's the secret to its success? |first=Dennis |last=Normile |date=17 March 2020 |doi=10.1126/science.abb7566}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"bbc24032020\">{{cite news |url=https://