cerated at [[Arkham Asylum]] meaning that someone else is posing as Man-Bat.\n* '''Villain:''' Man-Bat/[[Joker (character)|Joker]]\n|LineColor=000070\n}}\n}}\n\n=== Season 2 ===\nEpisode titles were revealed by [[Amazon (company)|Amazon]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/gp/video/detail/B0851V1LFF/ref=atv_dp_season_select_s2|title=Scooby Doo! And Guess Who: Season 2|accessdate=March 24, 2020|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|Amazon]]}}</ref> The air dates are unknown.\n\n{{Episode table |background=#000070 |overall=5 |season=5 |title=28 |aux1=20 |director=10 |writer=15 |airdate=36 |aux1T=Guest star(s) |episodes=\n\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=14\n|EpisodeNumber2=1\n|Title=The Nightmare Ghost of Psychic U!\n|DirectedBy=Frank Paur\n|WrittenBy=Caroline Farah\n|OriginalAirDate=\n|Aux1=[[Whoopi Goldberg]]\n|ShortSummary=While driving through snowy mountains, Mystery Inc. comes across a remote university where they meet Whoopi Goldberg who is a student at the university. Here, the gang must stop the university from closing before Whoopi can graduate, all while dealing with the Nightmare Ghost.\n\n* '''Villain:''' The Nightmare Ghost\n* '''Note:''' This episode premiered on September 24, 2019 on [[Boomerang (Italian TV channel)|Boomerang Italy]].<ref>{{cite web|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191004151111/https://tv.zam.it/programmitv_giorno.php?cat=Cartoni%20animati&data=2019-09-24&canali=sky|archive-date=October 4, 2019|url=https://tv.zam.it/programmitv_giorno.php?cat=Cartoni%20animati&data=2019-09-24&canali=sky|title=Cartoni animati in tv sky Marted\u00ec 24/09/2019|accessdate=October 4, 2019|publisher=Zam|language=Italian}}</ref>\n|LineColor=000070\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=15\n|EpisodeNumber2=2\n|Title=The Sword, The Fox, and the Scooby Doo!\n|DirectedBy=\n|WrittenBy=\n|OriginalAirDate=\n|Aux1=[[Mark Hamill]]\n|ShortSummary=\n|LineColor=000070\n}}\n{{Episode list\n|EpisodeNumber=16\n|EpisodeNumber2=3\n|Title=One Minute Mysteries!\n|Directed